  "title": "Calibration Specialist (up to $4K/mth w OT) #West #Oil&Gas #NJH",
  "description": "<p>Our client, a US MNC who provides chemical services andtechnology solutions for the hydrocarbon production, transmission, processing, and petrochemical industries, as well as consumer-focused markets.</p><p>They urgently requires<strong> </strong><u><strong>Contract Calibration Specialist</strong></u> to join them asap!</p><p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform routine tests and adjustments on various devices (pressure gauges, meters, micro-meters, calliper gauge etc.) to verify accuracy against established standards.</li></ul><ul><li>Create and maintain detailed records of calibration, test results, and equipment history; generate reports for management (Template provided)</li></ul><ul><li>Follow detailed calibration procedures and quality control protocols.</li></ul><ul><li>Conduct preventive maintenance, troubleshoot failures, and perform repairs on equipment to keep it within tolerance.</li></ul><ul><li>Manage calibration tools, supplies, and sometimes coordinate equipment servicing schedules.</li></ul><p>   <br /><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Min. 3 years of calibration experience</li><li>The role requires understanding of English for report reading & creation</li><li>Able to perform up to 40 hours of Overtime work per month</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Others:</strong></p><ul><li>Salary up to $2800 with Overtime payable</li><li>Able to start work from 7.30am to 3.15pm (standard work hours) from Mon to Fri</li><li>Location at Tuas area, door-to-door transport provided (to & fro)</li><li>12 months contract, renewable up to few years</li></ul><p><br />Interest applicants, pls email updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:jessie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">jessie@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Jessie Hoe Huey Miin</p><p>CEI Reg No. R1103861</p><p>EA Lic: 99C4599</p>",
